highlights.text: “傷情路” by Elanne Kong is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Hong Kong at #55.
“零距离的思念” by TINY 7 has been on Viral Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 140 days straight.
TENBLANK has the most spots on Viral Songs Hong Kong. “旋律と結晶” is the highest at #2.
“錯愛” by Elanne Kong is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Hong Kong, up 46 spots at #46.
